Subject: [PATCH 10/18] ARM: dts: imx6qdl-apalis-eval: disable PWM 1/2/3

PWM is not really required by Toradex Easy Installer and might
interfere on some carrier boards. Disable it by default.

Signed-off-by: Gerard Salvatella <gerard.salvatella@toradex.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6q-apalis-eval.dts | 12 ------------
 1 file changed, 12 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6q-apalis-eval.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6q-apalis-eval.dts
index 550409bc0825..de81050548a9 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6q-apalis-eval.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6q-apalis-eval.dts
@@ -290,18 +290,6 @@
 	status = "okay";
 };
 
-&pwm1 {
-	status = "okay";
-};
-
-&pwm2 {
-	status = "okay";
-};
-
-&pwm3 {
-	status = "okay";
-};
-
 &pwm4 {
 	status = "okay";
 };
